Class Director

java.lang.Object
com.kukrisports.movie.catalogue.model.common.CommonFields
com.kukrisports.movie.catalogue.model.Director
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity(name="directors") public class Director extends CommonFields
This class represents a Director in the movie catalog system. A director is responsible for creating movies and can be linked to multiple movies. This entity is stored in the "directors" table in the database. Each director has a name, a birthdate, an optional biography, and a list of movies theyâ€™ve directed. The name must be between 1 and 255 characters and cannot be blank. The birthdate is required and must be a valid date. The biography is optional but must not exceed 1000 characters if provided. This class also inherits createdAt and updatedAt timestamps from CommonFields.
